    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In Christi nomine, placuit atque convenit inter domnum <persName
                            ref="#people/1637" key="#Bishops">Obertum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopum</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/224" key="#Churches">episcopii sancte
                                <placeName ref="#places/58">Cremonensis</placeName>
                            <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs></orgName> nec non et inter
                                <persName><name ref="Wido de Melegnano">Guidonem</name></persName>
                        fìlium quondam <persName><name ref="Arialdus de Melegnano"
                            >Arialdi</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Ardericus de Melegnano">Ardericum</name></persName> filium
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Albertus de Melegnano"
                            >Alberti</name></persName> qui dicuntur de <placeName ref="#places/1941"
                            >Melegnano</placeName>, ut in Dei nomine ipse episcopus debeat dare
                        infrascriptis Guidoni et Arderico omnes <rs key="#Agricultural_renders"
                            >fructus et redditus</rs> et conditiones de loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/1936" key="#Curtes #Agricultural_renders #Honor"><geogName
                                ref="#estates/1527" key="#Curtes #Agricultural_renders #Honor"
                                >Foronovo</geogName></placeName> et <placeName ref="#places/1939"
                            key="#Curtes #Agricultural_renders #Honor"><geogName ref="#estates/1528"
                                key="#Curtes #Agricultural_renders #Honor"
                            >Barriano</geogName></placeName> et <placeName ref="#places/1940"
                            key="#Curtes #Honor"><geogName ref="#estates/1529"
                                key="#Curtes #Agricultural_renders">Mozanica</geogName></placeName>,
                        tam [infra quamque] et foris, quod ad ipsas <rs key="#Curtes">curtes</rs>
                        pertinet in integrum. Invicem infrascriptus Guido ed Ardericus dederunt
                        iamdicto episcopio omnes fructus et reddit]us et conditiones de loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/32"
                            key="#Curtes #Agricultural_renders #Feudum #Honor"><geogName
                                ref="#estates/38" key="#Curtes #Agricultural_renders #Feudum"
                                >Luciaria</geogName></placeName>, tam infra quamque et foris ad
                        ipsas curtem pertinens per <rs key="#Feudum">feodum</rs> [...]. Eo tamen
                        ordine, ut ipsi Guido et Ardericus et sui heredes ab hodie in antea usque ad
                        annos decem [habeant et teneant] fructus et redditus et conditiones de
                        infrascriptis locis Fornovo et Barriano et Mozanica cum omni <rs
                            key="#Honor">ho[nore </rs>ad ipsam curtem] pertinens in integrum, sine
                        contradictione episcopi suorum successorum. Invicem predictus episcopus et
                        sui suc[cessores habeant et tene]ant omnes fructus et redditus et
                        conditiones de ìnfrascripta curte Luciaria cum omni honore ad ipsam [ curtem
                        pertine]ns, sine contradictione infrascriptorum Guidonis et Arderici suorum
                        heredum. Insuper convenerunt inter se iamdict[i Guido et Arde]ricus cum
                        prefato episcopo, transacto infrascripto termino ut si placuerit episcopo in
                        antea tenere infrascriptam curtem Luc[iariam deb]eant vicissim ut supra
                        legitur, donec voluntas infrascripti episcopi fuerit vel eius successorum et
                        si ipse episcopus vel eius succesores hanc convenientiam noluerint tenere
                        tansacto infrascripto termino, tunc deb[eant ... ]. Penam vero inter se
                        posuerunt et spoponderut ut quis ex ipsis aut eorum heredes vel successores
                        de hac convenientia se subtraxerint, tunc componat pars parti fidem servanti
                            <rs key="#Penalty">penam argentum denarios bonos Mediolanenses libras
                            centum</rs>, et insuper infrascriptas curtes amittat. Factum est hoc
                        anno ab incarnacione domini nostri Iesu Christi .m0cxx0 • nono, indicione
                        octava. Unde duo breves uno tenore scripti sunt. Actum in loco Fornovo, in
                        solario episcopi, fìliciter, die veneris qui est tercio decimo die mensis
                        decembris. Signum + manus istorum Guidonis et Arderici qui hoc breve fieri
                        rogaverunt ut supra. Ibi fuerunt <persName key=" #Other_clerics #Witness"
                                ><name ref="Lantelmus">Lantelmus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Lanfrancus">Lanfrancus</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Bonomus">Bonomo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Iunius">Iunius</name></persName> et
                        <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Eribaldus Ferlinde Belexore">Ribaldus Ferlinde
                            Belexore</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Andreas de Leyco"
                                >Andrea de Leyco</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Rainerius"
                                    >Rainerius</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Arialdus de Caravagio et comes de Casino"
                            >Arialdus</name></persName> de Caravagio et <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>
                        de Casino et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Gosilinus">Gosilinus</name></persName> et
                        <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Alcherius de Vimercato"
                            >Alcherius</name></persName> de Vimarcato et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Arialdus">Airaldus</name></persName> filius <persName
                            key="#Count"><name ref="Albertus">Alberti</name></persName> comitis et
                        <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes de Montenaria">Iohannes de
                            Montenaria</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Obertus de Archidiano">Obertus</name></persName> de Archidiano
                        et reliqui plures rogati <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. <persName
                            key="#Judge #Missus_regis"><name ref="Otto">Otto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> ac <rs key="#Missus_regis">missus domini</rs>
                        quarti <persName ref="#people/77" key="#Emperor/king">Henrici</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperatoris</rs> interfui et subscripsi. Ego
                            <persName key="#Causidicus"><name ref="Obertus"
                            >Obertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Causidicus">causidicus</rs> interfui et subscripsi. Ego <persName
                            key="#Other_palatine_officer #Notary"><name ref="Wilielmus"
                                >Guilielmus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer"><rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> sacri
                            palacii</rs> interfui et hoc breve scripsi.</ab>
                </div>
